Hotel del' Annapurna


Named after Annapurna, the Goddess of Plenty and situated on an expanse of 5.5 acres, Hotel De L’Annapurna’s central location and proximity to the airport and the Royal Palace provides convenience and comfort for both leisure and business travelers. Embodying the true spirit of Nepal, this hotel provides a haven of relaxation amidst the city’s exhilarating cultural delights.

Annapurna provides the finest personal service and facilities in Kathmandu. The atmosphere is warm and relaxed and the ambience embraces the uniqueness of Nepalese culture. The variety of services offered will enable you to create your own experience.

The 150 room hotel includes 04 suites, 84 superior rooms and 62 standard rooms with modern amenities. The hotel specializes in Chinese, Indian and Continental cuisine. Complimenting the hotel’s services and facilities is The Cake Shop that offers the widest range of lip smacking cakes, pastries and confectionery products in the city.
 
For Further Information click Here.
